source:
Dear,

You are invited to join the {{subprogram_or_program_name}} {{as_role_name_articleized}} by {{invitor_name}}.

Once you have logged in for the first time and completed your profile, please take a few moments to check out the many ways you can interact with other program members: you can ask a question in the Q&A area (under "Advice" tab), participate in a discussion forum (under "Forums" tab), read and comment on an "article" posted by a member. We hope you have a wonderful mentoring experience. 

If you need any assistance, please contact me at admin@ementorprogram.org or by sending a message to "Admin" while logged into the system. We are so happy to have you participating in the program! 

Click here to accept the invitation and sign up for the {{subprogram_or_program_name}} {{as_role_name_articleized}}.
subject: Invitation: {{invitor_name}} invites you to join {{as_role_name_articleized}}
